org.lwjgl.ovr

Class OVRTrackingState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lwjgl.ovr.OVRTrackingState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pointer

    public final class OVRTrackingState
extends java.lang.Object
implements Pointer
    Tracking state at a given absolute time (describes predicted HMD pose etc). Returned by OVR.ovrHmd_GetTrackingState(long, double, java.nio.ByteBuffer).
